OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FEdinburgh sets date for    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fpavement parking ban       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Edinburgh city council has confirmed it
OL,6, will begin enforcing a ban on pavement 
OL,7, parking from January 29.               
OL,9,FIt had committed to be the first city  
OL,10,Fin Scotland to implement the ban, which
OL,11,Fcould see drivers who mount the kerb   
OL,12,Ffacing a #100 fine.                    
OL,14,FLocal authorities were given new powers
OL,15,Fby the Transport (Scotland) Act 2019,  
OL,16,Fwhich came into effect last month.     
OL,18,FParking at dropped kerbs and double    
OL,19,Fparking will also be banned, with an   
OL,20,Fexemption for delivery drivers.        
